docs {
  # Gemini Generate Content (External)

  Direct call to the Gemini REST API.
  Useful for verifying your GEMINI_API_KEY is valid.

  Set `{{GEMINI_API_KEY}}` in your Bruno environment or replace inline in the URL.

  ## Sample 200 Response

  ```json
  {
    "candidates": [{
      "content": {
        "parts": [{ "text": "Hello! How can I help you today?" }],
        "role": "model"
      }
    }]
  }
  ```
}
